## Disclaimer

The skills under category directories named after individuals (e.g. `addyosmani/`, `mattpocock/`, `superpowers/`) were aggregated from those authors' publicly published skill repositories. **The named authors are not affiliated with this repository, have not endorsed it, and do not maintain it.** Per-skill `source:` and `source_url:` frontmatter fields are progressively being added so each skill points back to its original source.

If you are an upstream author and would like a skill removed, renamed, or attributed differently, please open an issue.

